nce of winning...</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/itemrep/img/D-2aizsXhm-kpy0ffA4R--Xd07Y=/fit-in/246x300/pic2034769.jpg\" alt=\"Ghost Blitz game image\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Players</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Min. Age</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">2 - 8</td>\n<td align=\"right\">8</td>\n<td align=\"right\">20m</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","updatedAt":"2019-10-08T18:21:12.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"MunGell/awesome-for-beginners","categoryHTML":"<h2>Go</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/cockroachdb/cockroach/labels/good%20first%20issue\">CockroachDB</a> <em>(label: good first issue)</em> <br> The Scalable, Survivable, Strongly-Consistent SQL Database</li>","updatedAt":"2019-10-08T18:19:11.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"avelino/awesome-go","categoryHTML":"<h2>Machine Learning</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/gorgonia/gorgonia\">gorgonia</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/gorgonia/gorgonia\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":3999,\"repo\":\"gorgonia/gorgonia\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - graph-based computational library like Theano for Go that provides primitives for building various machine learning and neural network algorithms.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-10-08T17:49:29.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"sdras/awesome-actions","categoryHTML":"<h2>Community Resources</h2><h4>